data.description: We Rock the Spectrum Kids Gym is committed to providing a safe, nurturing, and fun environment for ALL KIDS, to foster learning, exploration and safe sensory experiences. We are committed to offering a place for events and special services for families and therapists, who are treating and working with kids on the spectrum, as well as their family and friends.
data.description_enriched: We Rock The Spectrum Kid's Gym is a kids indoor play gym located in tarzana, Ca. They provide a safe, nurturing, and fun environment for children to foster learning, exploration, and safe sensory experiences. They offer social skills groups and activities for children across the spectrum.
